# PokemonDBLoader

##### Goal:

To read a CSV file constaining details about Pokemon such as name, type, basic stats etc and load it into a MySQL database.

I will then use the [Java Database Connect]([https://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/jdbc/index.html](https://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/jdbc/index.html) library to connect the applicaiton to my MySQL instance for loading into the DB.
